title: Grant McLennan - Solo Albums
description:
Four Grant McLennan solo albums:

Watershed (1991)
Fireboy (1992)
Horsebreaker Star (1994) [US Single CD Version]
In Your Bright Ray (1997)

I found these golden nuggets very hard to come by, so when I did eventually find them, I thought I owed it to others out there looking for them to upload the buggers.

Please, please seed - this really is some great music.
